        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend the Individuals with Disabilities Education Act to clarify that the term "child with a disability" includes a child who needs special education and related services due to a health impairment resulting from Lyme disease or another tick-borne disease.</title>
